      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Congratulations!!


    You have made way to starting a sustainable line
    of food for your village. These simple but crucial first steps are key to learning
    how to create food for those in need. All with a balance diet kept in mind.


    You
    were not alone in this, help from the farmers made this possible. You were the
    vital part in keeping a community afloat in dire situations.


    Thanks for
